<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 25 Feb 2026 12:32:42 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>特朗普演讲期间比特币涨幅突破 66,000 美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-25/bitcoin-jumps-above-66-000-ahead-of-trump-s-address-to-congress</link><description>周三，在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普向国会发表国情咨文演讲期间，比特币在上午的上涨中顶住了持续的压力，削减了其亚洲早盘的部分涨幅。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i3cLAyNI9ELY/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Feb 2026 02:19:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-25/bitcoin-jumps-above-66-000-ahead-of-trump-s-address-to-congress</guid></item><item><title>利润、收入达到最高预期后，Circle 股价飙升</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-25/circle-s-shares-surge-after-profit-revenue-top-estimates</link><description>Circle Internet Group Inc.的利润和收入增长超过预期，其USDC稳定币流通量在第四季度猛增72%至753亿美元。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ia2nTk3DZthA/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Feb 2026 11:50:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-25/circle-s-shares-surge-after-profit-revenue-top-estimates</guid></item><item><title>比特币暴跌加剧了矿工之间的股市分裂</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-02-24/bitcoin-tumble-widens-stock-market-schism-among-miners</link><description>David Pan 撰写了快速发展的人工智能行业如何让股市投资者在比特币矿商中挑选赢家和输家的文章。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iMSyCna2RZAY/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Feb 2026 22:00:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-02-24/bitcoin-tumble-widens-stock-market-schism-among-miners</guid></item><item><title>随着数字货币的起飞，元测试稳定币支付</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-24/meta-testing-stablecoin-payments-as-digital-currencies-take-off</link><description>Meta Platforms Inc. 正在探索将稳定币支付集成到其应用程序中的方法，拥抱在线商务中越来越多使用的快速增长的数字货币形式。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/idnZFWFXbKsE/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Feb 2026 21:05:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-24/meta-testing-stablecoin-payments-as-digital-currencies-take-off</guid></item><item><title>随着买家的罢工，比特币的盈亏平衡陷阱正在扼杀每一次反弹</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-24/bitcoin-break-even-trap-is-killing-every-rally-as-buyers-strike</link><description>从加密货币顽固分子到首次 ETF 买家，那些通常会立即购买比特币的人却不敢这么做。数据解释了原因。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iUsowZmN6qHk/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Feb 2026 16:54:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-24/bitcoin-break-even-trap-is-killing-every-rally-as-buyers-strike</guid></item><item><title>据称，总部位于香港的稳定币支付公司 RedotPay 考虑在美国进行 10 亿美元的 IPO</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-24/hk-based-stablecoin-payments-firm-redotpay-is-said-to-consider-1-billion-us-ipo</link><description>据知情人士透露，总部位于香港的稳定币支付公司 RedotPay 正在考虑在美国进行首次公开​​募股，可能筹集超过 10 亿美元的资金。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iKF5JN79A6fc/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Feb 2026 06:19:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-24/hk-based-stablecoin-payments-firm-redotpay-is-said-to-consider-1-billion-us-ipo</guid></item><item><title>Crypto.com 表示其获得了美国银行执照的有条件批准</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-23/crypto-com-says-it-won-conditional-approval-for-us-bank-charter</link><description>Crypto.com 表示，它获得了美国国家信托银行执照的有条件批准，为数字资产交易所作为联邦监管机构提供加密服务铺平了道路。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iNMaZUKmmfxw/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Feb 2026 19:27:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-23/crypto-com-says-it-won-conditional-approval-for-us-bank-charter</guid></item><item><title>比特币恢复下滑，风险较高的资产失宠</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-23/bitcoin-btc-slides-to-65-000-in-latest-bout-of-tariff-uncertainty</link><description>由于对企业利润的新一轮担忧，加上美国关税挥之不去的不确定性，压制了全球市场的风险偏好，比特币交易价格接近近期交易区间的下限。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iUL.YM6dAtRE/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Feb 2026 01:55:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-23/bitcoin-btc-slides-to-65-000-in-latest-bout-of-tariff-uncertainty</guid></item><item><title>特朗普家族的加密货币企业表示面临“协同攻击”</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-23/trump-family-s-crypto-venture-says-it-faced-coordinated-attack</link><description>由特朗普家族支持的数字资产企业世界自由金融公司表示，它击败了针对其旗舰加密货币产品的未具体说明的“协同攻击”。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iRXduF0GEhmw/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Feb 2026 17:07:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-23/trump-family-s-crypto-venture-says-it-faced-coordinated-attack</guid></item><item><title>塞勒的策略再次依靠普通股购买比特币，同时推销优先股</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-23/bitcoin-buyer-strategy-leans-on-common-stock-while-pitching-preferred-shares</link><description>Michael Saylor 的 Strategy Inc. 过去一周在比特币上花费了约 4000 万美元，完全通过出售普通股为加密货币累积器的最新购买提供资金，尽管该公司向投资者推销其永久优先股。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i3KwS_ksASuw/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Feb 2026 15:03:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-23/bitcoin-buyer-strategy-leans-on-common-stock-while-pitching-preferred-shares</guid></item><item><title>币安的赵在特朗普家族加密货币盛会上吹捧美国的增长目标</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-23/binance-s-zhao-touts-us-growth-bid-at-trump-family-crypto-bash</link><description>在获得总统赦免几个月后，币安联合创始人赵长鹏上周出现在海湖庄园，将自己完全置于特朗普家族的加密货币轨道上。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iBBQhy.GWp0c/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Feb 2026 13:47:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-23/binance-s-zhao-touts-us-growth-bid-at-trump-family-crypto-bash</guid></item></channel></rss>